{"tid":1150294,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友呢排成日拒絕同我扑野","createTime":"2019-05-11T17:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T04:00:29.000Z","uid":176827,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"aaf6279d43d500cdbcc24bd0606b6d53133d5c19","tid":1150294,"uid":176827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T17:35:50.000Z","msg":"啱啱一齊個陣佢成日都要<br />\n見佢需要就算我唔想都會配合佢比佢要<br />\n呢個狀況持續左5-6個月<br />\n但呢排我有時同佢係間房攬攬錫錫都會想要<br />\n佢就話我大食又話好攰諸多籍口唔想做<br />\n已經拒絕左我好多次<br />\n我就諗明明我都係一個星期想要一兩次姐.係米我已經吸引唔到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：我同佢拍左一年拖.我第一次係比佢"},{"pid":"60a3b64d065232eb19b1b9e8a6b4347bb10c5cbc","tid":1150294,"uid":154357,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T17:36:31.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e700c4de0ab79275eba69a17ddb63e6e5cabb92d","tid":1150294,"uid":149357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T17:36:52.000Z","msg":"厭左"},{"pid":"1c027f250289d3bca85c9d1522b6842a639f961d","tid":1150294,"uid":38907,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T17:37:16.000Z","msg":"驚愛滋"},{"pid":"78e4cac0e9f36454dd74e75316b0818227c28510","tid":1150294,"uid":162095,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T17:38:08.000Z","msg":"自己打飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947f26e96cdc152a99853592b3586c44461ab21e","tid":1150294,"uid":129643,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T17:38:27.000Z","msg":"然後下個開咩渣男post就係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3533a2e4530db8eb00f9a2404caeb448fae72ace","tid":